# 📜 CHANGELOG (Pre-Release)

This changelog documents development progress prior to the official release of SecureAccess.

---

## [0.1.0] - 2025-07-10
### 🧪 Prototype Initiation
- Defined app concept: secure access control using proximity cards and biometric login.
- Created initial wireframes for login, dashboard, and user profile screens.
- Selected Firebase Authentication and Firestore as backend stack.

---

## [0.2.0] - 2025-07-18
### 🛠️ Core Functionality Development
- Implemented proximity card scanning and credential validation.
- Built basic login flow with Firebase integration.
- Developed user role assignment logic (admin, staff, guest).

---

## [0.3.0] - 2025-07-25
### 🧱 Infrastructure & Security
- Added input validation and secure authentication protocols.
- Configured Firestore rules for access control.
- Integrated TLS encryption for data-in-transit.

---

## [0.4.0] - 2025-08-01
### 📊 Dashboard & Analytics
- Created admin dashboard for real-time access monitoring.
- Designed Power BI dashboard mockups for access log visualization.
- Enabled access log storage and retrieval via Firestore.

---

## [0.5.0] - 2025-08-10
### 🧪 Testing & Refinement
- Conducted unit tests on login and access control modules.
- Refined UI for better responsiveness and accessibility.
- Fixed bugs related to role-based access logic.

---

## [0.6.0] - 2025-08-18
### 🚀 Final Prep Before Release
- Added biometric login option (fingerprint).
- Enabled offline mode with credential caching.
- Finalized wireframes and updated UI components.
- Conducted security audit and patched minor vulnerabilities.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-08-22
### 🎉 Official Release
- See full release notes in the main
